文献标识码：A

文章编号：2095-9931（2020）05-0101-10

Implementation Mechanism and Development Strategy on Information Exchange and Sharing of Container Rail-Sea Transport in China
Li Wei, Zhang Gai-ping, Zhang Wen-tao
(China Academy of Transportation Sciences, Beijing 100029, China)
Abstract：To meet the requirements of related parties for information exchange and sharing in multimodal transport and promote the development of multimodal transport in China, taking container railsea transport as an example, on the basis of reorganizing the international conventions and rules related to multimodal transport, railway and maritime transport, multimodal transport and related parties were

